==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hostess
<hw>Host"ess</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>hostesse</ets>, <ets>ostesse</ets>. See <er>Host</er> a
landlord.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A female host; a woman who hospitably
entertains guests at her house.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A woman who entertains guests for compensation; a
female innkeeper.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hostess-ship</ent>⟦br⟧
